Given I have Admin role
When I navigate to User Management
And I enter an email address not in the system
Then the system sends an invite link with tenant-scoped registration
And the new user is automatically assigned "Sales Representative" role
And they can only see data for our tenant

Given I attempt to delete a user with closed opportunities
When I click "Deactivate User"
Then the system reassigns their opportunities to me (Admin)
And sets the user to inactive (soft delete)